    public interface NetworkedElement
extends NameTag
    A representation of the model object 'Name Tagged Element'. Object with area, zone and owner arributes. It optionally holds a list of ref to CIM record. It has a sortNumber for storing sorting number. The intFlag is for storing some int for certain purpose, usually transient. visited attribute is for network walk through implementation

    The following features are supported:

    • Boolean Flag
    • Weight
    • Int Flag
    • Sort Number
    • Area
    • Zone
    • Owner
    See Also:
    NetPackage.getNetworkedElement()
